<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>This spell now applies the Mortal Strike debuff instead of applying a separate debuff with the same effect. This change will result in Drain refreshing the Mortal Strike effect rather than stacking with it.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The damage of this spell has been reduced to 90-495 (based on level), down from 100-550.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The cooldown of this spell has been increased to 180 seconds, up from 150.</li></ul>